=== A note on governance ===

LinkID can be deployed '''fully on WMF infrastructure''', with no dependency on external services.
It is available under the LPIL (Public Interest License) — free for Wikimedia, libraries, universities, and government.
This is not a product pitch. The goal is to design, together with the community, what a trustworthy and open reference persistence layer for Wikipedia should look like.
